      "_id": "aurilf2leg001",
      "_key": "!actors.items!aurilsecondform01.aurilf2leg001",
      "name": "Legendary Actions",
      "type": "feat",
      "img": "icons/svg/mystery-man.svg",
      "system": {
        "description": { "value": "Auril can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. Auril regains spent legendary actions at the start of her turn.\n\n<strong>Attack.</strong> Auril makes one weapon attack.\n<strong>Ice Flurry (Costs 2 Actions).</strong> Shards of ice whirl around Auril. Each creature within 30 feet of her takes 5 (2d4) piercing damage, and all nonmagical flames within 30 feet of Auril are extinguished.\n<strong>Splinter (Costs 3 Actions).</strong> Auril uses Create Ice Mephit, or she causes one ice mephit she can see within 60 feet of her to explode. Each creature within 10 feet of the exploding mephit must succeed on a DC 21 Dexterity saving throw or take 13 (3d8) piercing damage. The mephit is destroyed but doesn't use its Death Burst.", "chat": "" },
        "source": { "book": "Icewind Dale: Rime of the Frostmaiden" },
